      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exceptional vehicle maintained to the highest standard of automotive excellence. This unit remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. A rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast seeking an uncompromising driving experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
